import React from "react";
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import { Button, Card, CardBody, CardText, CardTitle, Col, Container, Form, FormGroup, Input, Label, Row } from "reactstrap";
function Signup(){
    return(
   <>
   <Container>
    <Row >
    <Col sm={{size:6,offset:3}}>
        <Card>
            <CardBody>
                <CardTitle>Create Account</CardTitle>
                <CardText>
                    <Form>
                        <FormGroup>

                             {/* Name Section */}
                            <Label for="Name">
                                Name
                             </Label>
                                <Input
                                id="Name"
                                placeholder="Enter your Name "
                                />

                             {/* School Id Section */  }
                             <Label for="SchoolId">
                                Email
                             </Label>
                             <Input
                                id="sid"
                                placeholder="Enter the Scool Id"
                             />

                             {/* Password Section */}
                             <Label for="Password">
                                Password
                             </Label>
                             <Input
                                id="password"
                                placeholder="Enter your Password"
                             />


                        </FormGroup>
                            <Button color="danger">
                            Signup

                            </Button>
                    </Form>

                </CardText>
                
            </CardBody>
        </Card>
    </Col>
        
    </Row>
   </Container>
   </>   
  

       
    )
}
export default Signup;
